00:08:09.860 --> 00:08:12.590
that's hard to make
accessible, or maybe even just

00:08:12.590 --> 00:08:14.487
like a regular DOM component.

00:08:14.487 --> 00:08:16.820
For the longest time, it's
been really, really difficult

00:08:16.820 --> 00:08:18.653
in some situations where
you have something,

00:08:18.653 --> 00:08:21.760
and in Canvas, it's
almost like a black box,

00:08:21.760 --> 00:08:24.330
but DOM it could be just
a really elaborate thing

00:08:24.330 --> 00:08:25.780
for something presentational.

00:08:25.780 --> 00:08:27.410
But now you can just hook in
there, and you can just say,

00:08:27.410 --> 00:08:28.220
you know what--

00:08:28.220 --> 00:08:28.880
SURMA: I know better.

00:08:28.880 --> 00:08:29.180
